      <section id="fs-id1322300" type="problems-exercises" class="problems-exercises"><title>Problems &amp; Exercises</title><exercise id="fs-id1394420" type="problems-exercises"><problem id="fs-id1394421">      <para id="import-auto-id1969478">What is the Fahrenheit temperature of a person with a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mtext>39</m:mtext><m:mtext>.</m:mtext><m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mtext>º</m:mtext><m:mtext>C</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math> fever?</para></problem>
<solution id="fs-id1425485">
      <para id="import-auto-id1969494"><m:math>
          
            <m:mrow>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mrow>
